text: Human female sexuality includes female sexual identity, sexual behavior and sexual activity. Human females may find having orgasms difficult and complicated. Some things related to human female sexuality are controversial. Overall, men are more commonly allosexual while women are more commonly demisexual.Borgogna, Nicholas C., et al.
